Rules for Recruiter

- Depends on cash collected
- We take total of cash collected
- calculation are based on cash collection
- if in any past month or current month total invoiced was 30K we use 3% other wise 2% on total collection
- - if 30K threshold reached + collection greater than 30K we payout 2% bonus next month.
